			(property "Description" "SEIKO ML414H-IV01E Reflowable Lithium Battery\n\nML414H is a rechargeable, coin type battery with features such as Pb-free reflowable (Peak temperature: 260 C) and high temperature heat resistance.\n\nBattery Characteristics:\n\n• 3.1V max voltage\n• Voff is 2V\n• 1mAH\n• 3k series resistor with battery\n• 72 hour charge time from 2.0-3.1V\n• 2.3-2.8V initial charge"
				(at 0 0 0)
