			(property "Description" "u-blox NEO-M9N GPS Module\n\nThe NEO-M9N module is built on the robust u-blox M9 GNSS chip, which provides exceptional sensitivity and acquisition times for all L1 GNSS systems. The u-blox M9 standard precision GNSS platform, which delivers meter-level accuracy, succeeds the well-known u-blox M8 product range. The receiver also provides higher navigation rate and improved security features compared to previous u-blox GNSS generations. The NEO-M9N module is available in the NEO form factor LLC package"
				(at 0 0 0)
